Localization.Name: Spirit of the Starman Statue
Localization.Description: Originally commissioned for the UEE Navy recruitment center in New York City on Earth, 'Spirit of the Starman' proudly displays an unnamed pilot, serving as a reminder of the solidarity and sacrifice the Empire's military demonstrate everyday as they serve as guardians of freedom and justice, and champions of honor and valor.
